_sText:
This is my first map. It is built with the exact same dimensions as the original poolday map, with some graphical improvements. Also, all the weapons in counter-strike excluding flash-bangs and smoke grenades are available on this map. There is a buy-zone and bombsite on the diving board. Finally, there is only one AWP which is in the swimming pool, and one Desert Eagle on the Diving Board.

Have Fun!
---------------------------------------------------------

This map is still in a early-beta stage.

Please contact me if you want to report any bugs, ask any questions, or if I forgot to credit anyone.

23 March, 2012
==================

After working on it for some time, the second beta is now available for download! Some improvements include:
- The addition of the missing MP5 on the CT's side
- The addition of the UMP45 for both T's and CT's
- The addition of cubemaps
- Smoothed some curves
- Toned down the HDR after receiving some complaints about it being too bright
- New custom sky (by komaokc)

18 April, 2012
==================

Beta 2 Update (Update #3):

-More textures
-Added Mirror
-Map Optimization
-Edited the toilet stall doors
-Minor improvements to detail geometry

Have fun!

26 May, 2012
==================

Due to other pressing concerns, the work on this map is indefinetly suspended.
